name: Those Days on The Road: A Revelation #1
description:
As Jack Kerouac said “There was nowhere to go but everywhere, so just keep on rolling under the stars.” 

I remember those days, where life didn’t stop you from move forward. As much as I remember, living on the road give you the light that you seek in the shadows that we sown from the past. And that’s what make you more human.

This is the beginning of the series ‘A Revelation’ from those days on the road.
